<div class="language-python line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="py" data-title="py"><pre v-pre class="language-python"><code><span class="line"><span class="token keyword">import</span> pandas <span class="token keyword">as</span> pd</span>
<span class="line"><span class="token keyword">import</span> imgkit</span>
